<br>
The reason Melee could never bind themselves is because originally noone was supposed to be able to be bound outside of a city, but back in wee old days of beta and original EQ, verant couldn't figure out how to make it so that people casting the spell on themselves couldn't be bound anywhere.  So...casters could bind, and thus bind anywhere, and melee couldn't.<br>
<br>
Since then Verant has started figuring out ways to limit where casters can bind as well.  I have no doubt that within 2 more years casters will have be bound in a city (and melee prolly won't have to be bound anywhere, they just appear with their gear =P ) <p><p><center><img src=http://lilyanaeq.homestead.com/files/Signatures/Aidon.jpg>
